---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="About — CA Accounting | AICPA-Member Firm in Glendale, CA"
  description="An AICPA-member accounting firm based in Glendale, California. Founded over twenty years ago by Farshid Khosravi, EA, and led with Managing Partner Narek Mkhitaryan, CPA."
>
  <section class="bg-cream-warm py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <p class="text-forest font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-6 fade-in">About</p>
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-serif text-navy leading-tight mb-6 fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
          A Glendale firm. Two credentialed partners. Twenty years of practice.
        </h1>
        <p class="text-charcoal text-lg leading-relaxed fade-in fade-in-delay-2">
          CA Accounting is a boutique accounting and tax firm headquartered on West Glenoaks Boulevard in Glendale, California. We serve clients across the state and beyond, with three industry specializations and the full range of services a growing business needs from its accounting partner.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Story -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16">
        <div class="fade-in">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif text-navy mb-6">How the firm came to be.</h2>
          <p class="text-charcoal text-base leading-relaxed mb-4">
            CA Accounting was founded by Farshid Khosravi, an Enrolled Agent — the highest credential the IRS issues to tax practitioners — with a vision for a firm built around two principles: deep technical expertise and long-term client relationships.
          </p>
          <p class="text-charcoal text-base leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Over the next two decades, the firm grew alongside its clients. Narek Mkhitaryan, CPA, joined as Managing Partner and brought a complementary discipline in audit, attestation, and corporate financial leadership. The team grew to eleven, and the practice deepened into the three industries — entertainment, medical, and real estate — that ask the most from a firm and reward depth most directly.
          </p>
          <p class="text-charcoal text-base leading-relaxed">
            Today, CA Accounting is an AICPA-member firm with a full suite of accounting, tax, and advisory services — and a client base that has, in many cases, been with us for ten years or more.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif text-navy mb-6">How we work.</h2>
          <p class="text-charcoal text-base leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Our approach is straightforward: every engagement is staffed by senior professionals and reviewed by a partner. There's no "junior associate learning your account every spring." The person who picks up the phone is the person doing the work.
          </p>
          <p class="text-charcoal text-base leading-relaxed mb-4">
            We invest in our team for the long term. Most of our staff has been with the firm for years — which means continuity, institutional memory, and the kind of trust that compounds quietly over time.
          </p>
          <p class="text-charcoal text-base leading-relaxed">
            And we hold ourselves to the standards of the AICPA — the professional body for certified public accountants in the United States. Membership isn't decorative. It's a commitment to a code of ethics, ongoing education, and quality control that informs how every engagement gets handled.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Partners -->
  <section class="bg-navy text-cream py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mb-16 fade-in">
        <p class="text-cream/60 font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Leadership</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-serif text-cream mb-6">
          The partners.
        </h2>
        <p class="text-cream/80 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Two credentials, two areas of expertise, one shared standard for client work.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        <div class="fade-in">
          <div class="aspect-square w-48 mb-6 overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-navy-deep">
            <img src="/images/team/farshid.jpg" alt="Farshid Khosravi, EA" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif text-cream mb-1">Farshid Khosravi, EA</h3>
          <p class="text-cream/60 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Founding Partner</p>
          <p class="text-cream/80 text-base leading-relaxed">
            Farshid founded CA Accounting and holds the Enrolled Agent designation — the IRS's highest credential for tax practitioners, granting unlimited practice rights before the IRS. He leads the firm's tax planning, IRS representation, and entertainment-industry work, and is the partner most clients first work with.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
          <div class="aspect-square w-48 mb-6 overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-navy-deep">
            <img src="/images/team/narek.jpg" alt="Narek Mkhitaryan, CPA" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif text-cream mb-1">Narek Mkhitaryan, CPA</h3>
          <p class="text-cream/60 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Managing Partner</p>
          <p class="text-cream/80 text-base leading-relaxed">
            Narek is a Certified Public Accountant and the firm's Managing Partner. He oversees attest and advisory work — including audits, reviews, compilations, and outsourced CFO engagements — and leads the firm's medical practice and real estate work. He's the partner clients turn to when the conversation moves from "compliance" to "strategy."
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values / Principles -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mb-12 fade-in">
        <p class="text-forest font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">What We Stand For</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif text-navy">
          Principles that show up in the work.
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        <div class="border-l-2 border-forest pl-6 fade-in">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-serif text-navy mb-3">Senior staffing on every engagement</h3>
          <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-base leading-relaxed">
            No client is handed off to a rotating cast of juniors. The professional working on your account knows your business, your industry, and your history.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-l-2 border-forest pl-6 fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-serif text-navy mb-3">Year-round, not just at deadline</h3>
          <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-base leading-relaxed">
            Tax planning happens before tax season. CFO advisory happens before the lender meeting. The work that pays off is the work done in advance.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-l-2 border-forest pl-6 fade-in">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-serif text-navy mb-3">Plain English over jargon</h3>
          <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-base leading-relaxed">
            We explain the trade-offs and the recommendations in language you can act on. If the answer is "it depends," we tell you what it depends on.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-l-2 border-forest pl-6 fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-serif text-navy mb-3">Long-term over short-term</h3>
          <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-base leading-relaxed">
            Most of our clients have been with us for years — some for more than a decade. We optimize for the relationship, not the engagement.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Client voice -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-24 bg-cream-warm">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <div class="card-elevated bg-white rounded-xl p-8 fade-in">
          <div class="text-forest/30 font-serif text-6xl leading-none mb-2 select-none" aria-hidden="true" style="font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 144;">"</div>
          <blockquote class="text-charcoal text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6 font-serif" style="font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 36;">
            His counsel is invaluable. What I value most about Farshid is his unimpeachable integrity.
          </blockquote>
          <div class="border-t border-line pt-4">
            <p class="text-navy font-semibold text-sm">Joe Cangelosi</p>
            <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm">Client</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card-elevated bg-white rounded-xl p-8 fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
          <div class="text-forest/30 font-serif text-6xl leading-none mb-2 select-none" aria-hidden="true" style="font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 144;">"</div>
          <blockquote class="text-charcoal text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6 font-serif" style="font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 36;">
            Trust is pre-eminent in any lasting and fulfilling relationship — and you've forged this bond of trust.
          </blockquote>
          <div class="border-t border-line pt-4">
            <p class="text-navy font-semibold text-sm">Jay Miller</p>
            <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm">Client</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center mt-12 fade-in">
        <a href="/testimonials" class="link-underline text-forest font-semibold text-sm">Read all client stories →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="bg-cream py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center fade-in">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif text-navy mb-6">
          Want to meet the team?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-charcoal text-base leading-relaxed mb-10">
          Schedule a free consultation. We'll listen to where your business is and tell you whether we're the right firm for the next chapter.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="btn-modern bg-forest text-cream font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded text-center hover:bg-forest-hover transition-colors"
          >
            Schedule a Free Consultation
          </a>
          <a
            href="/team"
            class="btn-modern border border-navy text-navy font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded text-center hover:bg-navy hover:text-cream transition-colors"
          >
            Meet the Team
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
